title: Celebrity Gossip Part 1 - Oprah Wasn't Going For A Bombshell Interview
description: We didn’t know that Drew Barrymore and Britney Spears were friends until Britney’s wedding, but Drew says she is actually very close with Britney. And Oprah says she didn’t expect her interview with Prince Harry and Meghan Markle to be a big deal.
